  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Displaced Families in the Northern Region</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will be addressing the needs of Iraqis displaced by the violence in northern Iraq. Support will be provided to displaced families to alleviate the suffering, promote stability and peaceful coexistence in northern Iraq.
Caritas will work on providing the following support:
-Providing psychological support and treating traumatic cases
-Creating opportunities for the children to continue their schooling
-Focusing on training the youth trying to provide them with job opportunities
-Accompanying the families in need of emergency aids
-Alleviating the suffering of the displaced families through different activities trying to rehabilitate them and disseminate the concepts of peace and peaceful coexistence.</narrative>
  </description>
